{"tid":921151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國頻傳AI詐騙 「用你的聲音你的臉，說你沒說過的話」","createTime":"2018-11-29T10:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T11:17:53.000Z","uid":28765,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"658a28c7c39b3910fdcf02fb7025f28bd312765a","tid":921151,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:32:54.000Z","msg":"2018-11-29 17:58<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕詐騙技術層出不窮，甚至開始利用高科技騙錢，中國有騙子透過人工智慧（AI）模仿他人的聲音、臉孔，「用你的聲音你的臉，說你沒說過的話」，成功把錢騙到手。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpklP71N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpklP71N.jpg&h=8cba8e12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國科技媒體談到，詐騙技術已與時俱進，已有一些人落入「微信語音」騙局。（路透）<br />\n<br />\n中國微信公眾號「極客視界」日前發表一篇文章「第一批AI已經開始詐騙」，談到詐騙技術已與時俱進，已有一些人落入「微信語音」騙局，一名趙姓女子近日收到父親的語音留言，稱買菜沒錢要趙女轉帳200人民幣，趙女確定是父親的口音後，就轉了錢，回到家才發現被騙了。蒼洲的王女也因「同學」透過語音留言借錢，被騙走500人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，這種騙局主要是因微信帳號被盜所致，雖然目前微信版本語音不能轉發，但騙子可透過提取語音文件或者安裝「增強版微信」，達到轉發語音的效果。就算打電話詢問，對方有可透過AI技術模仿出他人的聲音，「不同語氣情緒都能夠做到惟妙惟肖，足以以假亂真」。<br />\n<br />\n文章提到，開發這項技術的是谷歌2016年在加拿大蒙特婁大學建立的人工智慧研究實驗室（MILA），這款聲音合成技術Lyrebird，透過人工神經網路（Neural Network）和機器學習（Machine Learning），可以基於音色、音調、音節、停頓等多種特徵，來定義某個人的聲音，然後產生更加擬真的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，就算想透過視訊破解騙局，對方也可以透過AI偽造他人的臉孔進行詐騙。網路名稱為「deepfakes」的工程師，日前透過人工智慧換臉「FakeApp」程式，把好萊塢女星的臉移花接木到成人片女星身上，該技術甚至被應用於製造假新聞，引發不小爭議。<br />\n<br />\n文章表示，這兩項技術創立的初衷，並非為了作惡。Lyrebird創始人指出，他們希望藉此技術幫助那些發聲困難的人。deepfakes則說：「任何技術都可以被邪惡的動機利用，這種事情無法被禁止。我認為人人都可參與機器學習研究不是一件壞事。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2628098\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2628098&d=JMapTl%2F%2BfFbrePG30TsOpf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=53a1adf0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2628098&h=40fa486f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2628098</a>"},{"pid":"72e73a3ff22dcbedd3608d3c95b9c1eddedbdc0f","tid":921151,"uid":198583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:33:32.000Z","msg":"又屈中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a944f32d1f13e0db3b3ae0cf4ca2631665aeeda","tid":921151,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:34:12.000Z","msg":"科技強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756fb16a533691565655d6ae45c84bc37b6f163b","tid":921151,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:36:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文章提到，開發這項技術的是谷歌2016年在加拿大蒙特婁大學建立的人工智慧研究實驗室（MILA）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n咩都偷得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d226fc1f74b519c5795f9e48aa5a8ac6b181f327","tid":921151,"uid":79959,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YJixGSm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYJixGSm.jpg&h=d67c46a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07b590cfe22d4310f24030199d731d8766a5e140","tid":921151,"uid":78470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:49:46.000Z","msg":"偷個技術黎呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb07ca8a13514f6ae54ba2bc8f16692a52ee7606","tid":921151,"uid":44870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T10:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/2015